ws/admin/2010/08/4c7cbc5800369_square.jpg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbc5800369_thumbnail.jpg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbc5800369_small.jpg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbc5800369_crop.jpg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbc5800369_medium.jpg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbc5800369_large.jpg','active',2,'2010-08-31 15:26:31',1,'admin',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'admin','2010-08-31 15:26:42',0,0,0,0,NULL,0,'vi_VN'),(21,1,'Da Lat','','da-lat','<p>Da Lat, or Dalat, (pop. 197,000 as of 2007[update], spelled Ä�&agrave; Láº¡t in Vietnamese) About this sound pronunciation (help&middot;info) is the capital of L&acirc;m Ä�á»“ng Province in Vietnam.</p>','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde84daa7_crop.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Tuyá»�n L&acirc;m Lake in the morning fog&nbsp; </em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The city is located 1,500 m (4,900 ft) above sea level on the Langbiang Plateau in the southern parts of the Central Highlands (in Vietnamese, T&acirc;y Nguy&ecirc;n). In Vietnam, Ä�&agrave; Láº¡t is a popular tourist destination.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde95d244_crop.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><small>Outside Da Lat Market at night</small></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ä�&agrave; Láº¡t\'s specific sights are pine wood (forming the name: \"City of thousands of pine trees\") with twisting roads and tree marigold (Vietnamese: d&atilde; quá»³) blossom in the winter. The city\'s temperate weather stands in contrast to Vietnam\'s otherwise tropical climate. Mist covering the valleys almost year-round leads to its name \"City of eternal spring.\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde738539_crop.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Da Lat\'s Market square at night</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ä�&agrave; Láº¡t is also known as an area for science research in the fields of biotechnology and nuclear physics.<br /><br />With its year-round cool weather, Ä�&agrave; Láº¡t supplies temperate agriculture products for all over Vietnam, for example, cabbage and cauliflower. Its flower industry produces two typical flowers: hydrangea (Vietnamese: cáº©m t&uacute; cáº§u) and golden everlasting (Vietnamese: hoa báº¥t tá»­). The confectionery industry offers a wide range of má»©t, a kind of fruit preserve made from strawberry, mulberry, sweet potato, and rose.</p>','Wikipedia','','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_square.jpeg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_thumbnail.jpeg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_small.jpeg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_crop.jpeg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_medium.jpeg','http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_large.jpeg','active',3,'2010-08-31 15:30:10',1,'admin','2010-08-31 15:43:17',1,'admin',1,'admin','2010-08-31 15:30:17',0,0,0,0,NULL,0,'en_US'),(22,13,'Ä�Ã  Láº¡t','','da-lat','<p>Ä�&agrave; Láº¡t l&agrave; má»™t th&agrave;nh phá»‘ trá»±c thuá»™c tá»‰nh v&agrave; tá»‰nh lá»‹ tá»‰nh L&acirc;m Ä�á»“ng, náº±m tr&ecirc;n cao nguy&ecirc;n L&acirc;m Vi&ecirc;n, á»Ÿ Ä‘á»™ cao 1.500 m so vá»›i máº·t nÆ°á»›c biá»ƒn v&agrave; diá»‡n t&iacute;ch tá»± nhi&ecirc;n: 393,29 km&su